stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Setup : connect + mint + delegate
  Setup --> Created : proposeWithDeposit
  Created --> Pending : delay 1 block
  Pending --> Active : voting open
  Active --> Closed : voting period end

  Closed --> Succeeded : quorum >= 60% and for > against
  Closed --> Defeated : otherwise

  Succeeded --> Executed : execute
  Defeated --> [*]
  Executed --> [*]
